  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinaryFunction<L,R,L>, java.util.function.Function<L,L>, Relatable

    public class BinaryFunctionGroup<L,R>
extends AbstractBinaryFunction<L,R,L>
    A binary function implementation that groups an arbitrary number of binary functions and applies all of them successively to input values in the same order in which they are added to the group.
